Background:
Ethan is a dedicated and experienced project manager who has built a reputation for his ability to navigate complex technical projects with ease. With a background in engineering, he has honed his skills in coordinating cross-functional teams, mitigating risks, and delivering successful outcomes for his clients.

Demographics:
