Financial Situation:
Ethan's steady income as a project manager allows him to maintain a comfortable lifestyle while also prioritizing long-term financial security. He is disciplined in his budgeting and savings, ensuring that he can comfortably cover his living expenses and invest in his future. While Ethan enjoys the occasional splurge, such as a family vacation or a new piece of technology, he is generally mindful of his spending and focused on building wealth through prudent financial management.

